title: Bug 134040: Row should not have page break property in Property Editor now.
description: When setting the pageBreak properties in the Property Editor, the expected result is that the row should not have the page break property. However, the actual result is that the page break can be set to the row in the Property Editor, but it cannot be saved.
OB: The expected behavior is that the row should not have the page break property in the Property Editor.
EB: Currently, the row in the Property Editor can have the page break property set, but it cannot be saved.
SR: Investigate and fix the issue in the Property Editor where the page break property can be set for the row, but it cannot be saved.
